The following graphs/tables combine data from the following samples:

  • Recruited on 6/8/21, 5 participants (no IRI data)
  • Recruited on 1/31/22, 20 participants
  • Recruited on 2/21/22, 21 participants
  • Recruited on 05/23/22, 31 participants

Exclusions computed 05/26/22

Total n = 79

  1. filter out people who don’t get all 4 qualtics attention correct (5 people, n = 74)
  2. filter people who dont pass 14/16 threshold for EAEA questions (17 people, n = 57)
  3. filter people who didn’t move the slider bar for at least 1 video (2 people, n = 55)
  4. filter people who didn’t complete digit span task (1 person, n = 54)
  5. filter people who have digit span forward score greater than 2 sds of the mean (4, n = 50)
  6. filter people who have digit span reverse score greater than 2 sds of the mean (1, n = 49)
